Class Achievement

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Achievement
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    IOnLevelAchievement, LoadedAchievement, OnMoveAchievement

    public abstract class Achievement
extends java.lang.Object
    System for achievements. Based loosely around the Move classes from SolitairePluginTutorial in that each Achievement will know how to verify itself.
